   "source": [
    "# M4 MultiHead Training - CTC + SAR Hybrid Approach\n",
    "\n",
    "⚠️ **TRAINING FROM SCRATCH - MultiHead Architecture**\n",
    "\n",
    "**Target**: Reduce 6→0 error rate from 20.4% to <5%\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🎯 Architecture: MultiHead (CTC + SAR)\n",
    "\n",
    "### **CTC Head** (Connectionist Temporal Classification)\n",
    "- Đơn giản, nhanh, ổn định\n",
    "- Tốt cho recognition cơ bản\n",
    "\n",
    "### **SAR Head** (Show, Attend and Read)\n",
    "- Attention mechanism để focus vào từng digit\n",
    "- Tốt cho các digit khó phân biệt (6 vs 0)\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🔧 CRITICAL FIXES APPLIED:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Tăng Input Width**: 256 → Đủ sequence length cho CTC\n",
    "2. **Stride Fix**: (2,2) → (2,1) → Giữ width, chỉ giảm height\n",
    "3. **SOS Token**: Index 11 (không conflict với digit 0)\n",
    "4. **Num Classes**: 12 (0-9 digits + blank + SOS)\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "**Expected Results:**\n",
    "- 6→0 error rate: 20.4% → <5%\n",
    "- Overall accuracy: 85-90%\n",
    "- Training time: ~45-60 minutes on GPU T4"
   ]
  },
